title: BRIEF-EC2 sees FY 2015 net profit of 1.1 mln zlotys
text:
BRIEF-EC2 sees FY 2015 net profit of 1.1 mln zlotys Sept 14 
Sept 14 EC2 SA : 
* Sees FY 2015 net profit of 1.1 million zlotys ($296,400) 
* Sees FY revenue in 2015 at 5.5 million zlotys, in 2016 at 7.3 million zlotys and in 2017 at 9.5 million zlotys Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 3.7108 zlotys) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
